(21, 'Chao cac ban cua Toi.', '<p>Xin gui loi chao den toan the cac ban thuoc To Network .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toi tham gia forum nham muc dich tim hieu them ve cac hinh thuc giao nhan door thong qua network . Cac ban am hieu nhieu xin vui long chia se mot so thong tin sau :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1/.Co bao nhieu hinh thuc giao nhan duoc thuc hien thong qua cac dai ly tai nuoc ngoai . Cu the cac loai hinh dich vu ay .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2/.Lam sao de co the chuyen mot lo hang bat ky tu London - Anh Quoc ve TPHCM va khach hang se tra tien tai VN . Vui long huong dan cu the de khach hang hieu ro ve dich vu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Than chao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 3, '2013-12-16 15:27:42', '2013-12-16 15:27:42', 'huynhhai', '', 0),
